headline: 2 Reasons to Like ADP and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Since October 2024, ADP has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 3.3% while floating around $282.69. However, the stock is beating the S&P 500’s 10% decline during that period.
